title: There are two types of content!
pid: 1fa1fa5f-6bb5-49bb-bc62-a51a0e599b11
body: |2-
  View-content is the relationship that this node
  belongs to the (or the primary, for ViewOf_GraphNode)
  collection implied by the parent. 

  With this, parentIs no longer needs a separate contains indicator
  for graphnodes and partner collections.
